{"tid":2225531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林志偉: 獲授勳原因很簡單 過去一年多竭盡所能維護香港法治","createTime":"2020-10-01T11:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T14:11:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"50b1f5175a2843403d1d3faeb3338ce266063130","tid":2225531,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:37:31.000Z","msg":"687名獲授勳人士當中有106人是現職或前警員，當中12人於去年反修例衝突執勤受傷，獲頒銀英勇及銅英勇勳章，包括在觀塘港鐵站被人用利器割頸的警長梁兆祥，以及懷疑被鋼珠射爆牙的高級督察黃家倫。國安處高級警司李桂華、警察隊員佐級協會主席林志偉獲頒香港警察榮譽獎章。林志偉表示：「原因很簡單。過去一年多，我們警隊竭盡所能維護香港法治，保護香港市民。當然高興，但會平常心，多謝警隊推薦和政府的承認。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/36716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F36716&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w17Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=f0b2e081\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F36716&h=b879ce5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/36716</a>"},{"pid":"f12ea698d61e2f9816f48eb4123c0e654c4c1669","tid":2225531,"uid":105790,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:39:16.000Z","msg":"無個個樣正常"},{"pid":"78de60453426fbfb3433ab0515fe765c4153c67a","tid":2225531,"uid":14422,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:41:28.000Z","msg":"策劃67暴動、爆死兩個細路嘅恐怖分子頭目 楊光都拎大紫荊啦<br />\n同樣係恐怖分子頭目嘅林志偉拎有咩出奇？應該做埋國家主席添啦"},{"pid":"3f369041b4f5728792a3b1aae3eeefefa14b84df","tid":2225531,"uid":181321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:47:26.000Z","msg":"無所謂啦<br />\n一個被國際制裁嘅恐怖份子政權頒贈嘅獎項都係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91958189991ab532517af82776dd64f6dc9bf249","tid":2225531,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" clas